text: Pankaj Singh may refer to: Pankaj Singh (Assistant manager operations) (born 02 Feb 1990) *Pankaj Singh (cricketer) (born 6 May 1985) is an Indian cricketer. *Pankaj Singh (politician) (born 12 December 1978) is an Indian politician who is BJP's General Secretary for Uttar Pradesh.
title: Pankaj Singh
